gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;admonition-content mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-inherit&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;I used this very handy website to generate logo and favicon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
